to know how much you’re absorbing and which

214
00:27:39,120 --> 00:27:48,580
of the areas that need to be corrected or
where you need to focus your attention on

215
00:27:48,580 --> 00:28:01,450
to get a better understanding.” It’s something
like that, that on the superficial level these

216
00:28:01,450 --> 00:28:05,970
things are objectionable to us. But Guru Mahārāja
is saying, “In the Bhāgavatam it says not

217
00:28:05,970 --> 00:28:11,789
