form they knew he was advanced and enlightened

237
00:30:44,380 --> 00:30:51,220
soul, and additionally he was legendary already.

238
00:30:51,220 --> 00:30:58,340
In the time of Śrīla Gaura-Kiśora Dās
Bābājī Mahārāja, like: bhaktāvadhūta

239
00:30:58,340 --> 00:31:03,390
mūrttaye, Guru Mahārāja says in praṇām
to him, one of the praṇāms to him. Like

240
00:31:03,390 --> 00:31:15,570
in avadhut people, as young boys do — they
mock, they tease, they make fun, they throw

241
00:31:15,570 --> 00:31:21,679
things. Imagine, they’re doing that to Śrīla
Gaura-Kiśora Dās Bābājī Mahārāja. Sometimes

242
00:31:21,679 --> 00:31:31,519
we think like, “Why am I being treated like
