protected by Krishna, this thing, another.

246
00:31:47,669 --> 00:31:52,610
We see that they’re visited by illness from
time to time.) And [Śrīla] Gurudev said

247
00:31:52,610 --> 00:31:58,740
to them, “No, actually it’s the opposite.
Because they are escaping Maya, she’s trying

248
00:31:58,740 --> 00:32:05,950
harder to get them.” So, we will see it
visited upon them even more, not the opposite.

249
00:32:05,950 --> 00:32:14,470
Vamśī Dās Bābājī Mahārāja also said
in his final days (and he was diseased in

250
00:32:14,470 --> 00:32:17,120
so many ways as Guru Mahārāja said). He
turned [INDISTINCT] to me and would go [INDISTINCT],

251
00:32:17,120 --> 00:32:23,249
“This is your vaiṣṇava? Look at me.
Look at what’s happened to me.” But Guru

252
00:32:23,249 --> 00:32:28,070
Mahārāja said, as a way of saying, “Don’t
