255
00:32:44,330 --> 00:32:48,799
And what to speak of such an exalted soul
as [Śrīla] Gaura-Kiśora Dās Bābājī

256
00:32:48,799 --> 00:32:54,090
Mahārāj — they mocking him, throwing things
at him. But Guru Mahārāja said, “His response

257
00:32:54,090 --> 00:33:02,740
was, rather than some ego abhimān come, and
chastising those [children]: ‘do you know

