smiling face and friendly hand of Krishna

282
00:36:03,870 --> 00:36:13,410
in the background.” And we are here for
spiritual culture as someone saying, “Oh,

283
00:36:13,410 --> 00:36:20,930
that’s the greater souls… How?” You
have to begin somewhere and this is the advice

284
00:36:20,930 --> 00:36:36,240
that’s being given to us. Maybe with tears
in our eyes or a heavy heart we may adopt

285
00:36:36,240 --> 00:36:39,660
this angle of vision for some relief.

286
00:36:39,660 --> 00:36:49,970
Goswāmī Mahārāja: Yes, anything else?
Nityānanda Dās: There is one question from

287
00:36:49,970 --> 00:36:58,130
