323
00:42:05,760 --> 00:42:06,930
of that.

324
00:42:06,930 --> 00:42:14,250
So, for example, in Śrīla Bhakti Siddhānta
Saraswatī Thakur’s concluding words of

325
00:42:14,250 --> 00:42:24,410
