347
00:45:16,220 --> 00:45:19,210
Mahāprabhu is saying:
… pāda-paṅkaja-

348
00:45:19,210 --> 00:45:20,710
sthita-dhūlī-sadṛśaṁ vichintaya

349
00:45:20,710 --> 00:45:29,980
[Śrīla] Prabhupāda would say, “As a particle
of dust at your holy lotus feet.” What does

350
00:45:29,980 --> 00:45:37,480
that mean? Why the word ‘dust’? Because
we understand dust that the least aspect right

351
00:45:37,480 --> 00:45:45,180
