Uddhava.” And what does that Uddhava say?

362
00:46:56,460 --> 00:46:59,760
āsām aho charaṇa-reṇu-juṣām ahaṁ
syāṁ

363
00:46:59,760 --> 00:47:05,940
vṛndāvane kim api gulma-latauṣadhīnām
yā dustyajaṁ sva-janam ārya-pathaṁ cha

