370
00:47:46,550 --> 00:47:55,010
The motto of Śrī Gaudia Math as composed
and sung by Śrīla Saraswatī Ṭhākur:

371
00:47:55,010 --> 00:48:02,910
pujala rāga-patha gaurava-bhange matala saru
-jana visaya range. Pujala rāga. Rāga-mārga

