am api kalayantīṁ prāṇa-koṭer abhīṣṭam

381
00:49:15,060 --> 00:49:21,960
pramudita-madirākṣī-vṛnda-vaidagdhya-dīkṣā-gurum
ati-guru-kīrtiṁ rādhikām archayāmi

